    <briefdescription>
<para>Interface publique du driver Radar HLK-LD6002 — UART + TinyFrame. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Le driver utilise le ring buffer UART installé par <ref refid="group__group__hw__diag_1gad0805242746ecf8545068878b9433eeb" kindref="member">hw_diag_run()</ref> (uart_driver_install sur UART_NUM_2). Il parse le protocole TinyFrame : SOF(0x01) | Type(2o) | Longueur(1o) | Données | EOF(0x04)</para>
<para>Types reconnus : 0x0A14 → breath_rate_bpm (uint16 big-endian) 0x0A15 → heart_rate_bpm (uint16 big-endian) 0x0A16 → target_distance_mm (uint16 big-endian) </para>
    </detaileddescription>
